snippet: Five students were shot near an Atlanta high school on Tuesday afternoon, although none of the injuries were life threatening, the police said
abstract: Five students are shot near an Atlanta high school, although none of the injuries are life threatening; it is not known whether someone is in custody, and a motive has not been established.
lead_paragraph: Five students were shot near an Atlanta high school on Tuesday afternoon, although none of the injuries were life threatening, the police said
